<h1>In Plain English</h1>
<p>&nbsp;In Plain English is a technology-focused media company established in 2018 by Sunil Sandhu. Since its founding, it has grown into a widely recognized platform that publishes educational and accessible content aimed at helping people understand complex technical topics. The platform is home to several well-known publications, including JavaScript In Plain English, Python In Plain English, and Stackademic, which together cover a broad range of subjects within software development and modern technology.</p>
<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://plainenglish.io/" ><img border="0" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgf1_g4O72hgq0WSvbtQvku-1BRDbyfBDr7G4p5H1UXiYWmjoz5yjMQASsTIyNg7Ay5ryDoWXyzftrya1OkxQ1qaf24AZEs99JP5mad9_GZ3yDdPKjtcjOBmr-QbryZwo_MtxS30-V-65tPuOBvamENr4xi2TDHfhAXEM2LsiGkm5VHCv592D33K6sCkmk/s150/EW8kCS9l_400x400.jpg" /></a></div>
<p>&nbsp;Over time, the platform has attracted tens of thousands of contributors from around the world. More than 50,000 writers have collectively produced over 80,000 to 100,000 articles, contributing to a large and diverse knowledge base. These articles are designed to simplify technical concepts, making them easier to understand for readers at all levels, from beginners to experienced developers. The goal has always been to make education more accessible and practical.</p>
<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://plainenglish.io/" ><img border="0" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgjxTbvgS9qsZDwy4Dvz3ilurtc7BokBFChEs5-2zwZSiTLh8p3bF-1ly-nPI-hmGv9eKSSLZU-gQ7mD4tZg_Ep-23xkfqh01C6V9S616S0L0RAhEQPkIN-ZoOO7ed3oDrXWOiI3-qIfYOKUChPVuuRdNiNjyhnXkUEj_v8IahxBsjZX1696JAxZr0QrpU/s16000/1500x500.jpg" /></a></div>
<p>&nbsp;In Plain English has achieved a significant global reach, with readers from over 190 to 200 countries engaging with its content. Across all its publications, the platform has surpassed 200 million views, demonstrating its influence and popularity within the tech community. On a monthly basis, it continues to attract millions of readers, with estimates ranging from 3 million to 3.5 million views each month.</p>
<p>&nbsp;The platform covers a wide range of topics, including artificial intelligence, frontend and backend development, JavaScript, Python, cloud infrastructure, Web3 and cryptocurrency, data analytics, mobile development, security, design, developer tools, and career growth. This variety allows readers to explore different areas of technology and stay updated with the latest trends and tools.</p>
<p>&nbsp;In addition to long-form guides and technical deep dives, the platform also provides practical resources such as explainers, tutorials, and quick-reference materials. These are aimed at helping developers learn efficiently and apply their knowledge in real-world scenarios. The content is regularly updated, with new articles covering emerging technologies, industry practices, and developer experiences.</p>
<p>&nbsp;In Plain English continues to serve as a learning hub for developers worldwide, offering content that supports both skill development and career growth. Its mission remains centered on empowering people through clear, accessible, and educational content, making technology easier to understand for a global audience.</p>
